data.description: HUGE home in North Hanford, Ca. featuring 3,899 sq ft on a 16,300 sq ft lot with swimming pool and finished basement & Owned Solar. Features include a large living room with laminate flooring and a wall of windows that allow natural light, a den area with a fireplace and dining area with tiled floors and a kitchen are an abundance of cabinets, spacious counters and a double oven. Just off the kitchen is a utility room with built in grill, laundry area, a pantry and half bath. One bedroom has a full bathroom near the front of the house, the 4 other bedrooms and hall bath are located down the hall. The basement is accessed from the hallway and has a large main room with multiple sub-rooms ( some with built in storage) that can be reimagined. Outdoors is possible RV parking and a large backyard.  This home is sold AS IS, so open your mind to it's possibilities.
